{"tid":2174000,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[日本][簡單] 日式醬油焗三文魚柳","createTime":"2020-08-25T15:03:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T16:02:42.000Z","uid":113525,"like":116,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"bf96eeba0d9111c3cf74614d844a33cc438f3eb3","tid":2174000,"uid":113525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T15:03:59.000Z","msg":"今次整既焗三文魚柳 簡單 超好食 帶飯一流 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n製成品<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YNrSbWC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYNrSbWC.jpg&h=d69684ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三文魚柳 去皮 洗淨 印乾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4zVC7vf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4zVC7vf.jpg&h=e4916ff5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yPTtuJD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyPTtuJD.jpg&h=9f8084fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n預備薑蓉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MOa0kQH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMOa0kQH.jpg&h=14cb6f7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n將日式醬油、味醂、清酒和薑蓉加入碗入面，攪勻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vVDdFQ5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvVDdFQ5.jpg&h=06b4b279&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n將三文魚柳放入保鮮袋，倒碗汁入去，醃大約一個鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uaa324H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUaa324H.jpg&h=c2af050a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n醃好之後，預熱焗爐到180度，焗8-10分鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BGPPYDm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBGPPYDm.jpg&h=fcc3ddbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n焗緊果陣，我地可以煮返熱個汁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OmFzqiH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOmFzqiH.jpg&h=dbac5599&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n淋汁上面，放埋三文魚子同鰹魚片上去，食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/viJJiEd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FviJJiEd.jpg&h=cd9045d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vEq0k0e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvEq0k0e.png&h=92947180&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食評: 焗既三文魚食落口好滑，食落個喉嚨好c服 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有興趣既可以睇下條片同埋記得訂閱我呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/x7xAilgJXrQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fx7xAilgJXrQ&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDnaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=ac047edb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/x7xAilgJXrQ</a><br />\nIG :<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/eatingaroundthe_World/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Featingaroundthe_World%2F&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDnaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=b5593014\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/eatingaroundthe_World/</a><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈電影《幻愛》本周五重新上映, 跪求手足撐場支持.<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2173820\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2173820</a>"},{"pid":"4546be5996360b6e99a97dda960914d380404540","tid":2174000,"uid":299794,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T15:05:10.000Z","msg":"Why走皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"b6336a7d1aa4de1e42d6f5d2aa6e92ae49b34cb8","tid":2174000,"uid":113525,"like":2,"dislike":20,"score":-18,"quote":{"pid":"4546be5996360b6e99a97dda960914d380404540","tid":2174000,"uid":299794,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T15:05:10.000Z","msg":"Why走皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T15:08:38.000Z","msg":"懶得打鱗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5062a0cedac083285369ef30461e4c74dd154f7d","tid":2174000,"uid":113525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T15:09:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dc5bb40bb1ef2c5cc58f03c64b3f9167e61897e0","tid":2174000,"uid":113525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T15:09:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"296672d624ef8137f68d49f25b283f1eb6eb7092","tid":2174000,"uid":13308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T15:11:20.000Z","msg":"正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a86181f389c79e34a4d53eba592c06f9633a830d","tid":2174000,"uid":194483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T15:13:52.000Z","msg":"水聲好清脆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7ea30b146fab34551e9785464f4e5cc2660d81","tid":2174000,"uid":113525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"296672d624ef8137f68d49f25b283f1eb6eb7092","tid":2174000,"uid":13308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T15:11:20.000Z","msg":"正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T15:14:41.000Z","msg":"真係 好滑好好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dec4986dc6a32bb669bef91963ed059e51a5eb7","tid":2174000,"uid":105232,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T15:18:44.000Z","msg":"竟然去皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最好食就係塊皮"},{"pid":"3ac4904f8ffbdc79bb5bce91cd4f009847aad9a1","tid":2174000,"uid":113525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a86181f389c79e34a4d53eba592c06f9633a830d","tid":2174000,"uid":194483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T15:13:52.000Z","msg":"水聲好清脆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T15:18:44.000Z","msg":"係 清脆師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a13b2f239174808b7a02cb8d5b7d0d0668de84f9","tid":2174000,"uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T15:27:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a019da035150a061011905d834fe89613c80672e","tid":2174000,"uid":113525,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"2dec4986dc6a32bb669bef91963ed059e51a5eb7","tid":2174000,"uid":105232,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T15:18:44.000Z","msg":"竟然去皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最好食就係塊皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T15:30:42.000Z","msg":"焗塊皮應該冇咁好食 <br />\n煎既皮真係不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00cc192721604f6995a8b3f82c0dedd2a9477f31","tid":2174000,"uid":122083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"s